X-Men - Magik - Storm & Illyana HC (2008) (Minutemen-Bluntman)


The hardcover collection of X-Men: Storm And Illyana 1-4 tells the tale of Illyana Rasputin, the younger sister of the X-Man Colossus. Rediscover a world of magic, mutants, and demons as Illyana struggles against the sorcerer Belasco, with the aid of alternate reality versions of Storm and Kitty Pryde. Will Illyana prevail against the impossible odds against her, and return home to her family and friends? And if so, what is to become of her?
